---
const layers = [
  ["Layer 0", "方向与路由", "组织规则、项目地图、角色与关键约束"],
  ["Layer 1", "工作速查", "当前任务直接相关的模块、流程与决策"],
  ["Layer 2", "深层事实", "代码、文档、历史、来源与完整业务规则"]
];
---

<section class="knowledge-section section" id="knowledge">
  <div class="container knowledge-grid">
    <div class="knowledge-art" data-reveal>
      <div class="knowledge-axis" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      {layers.map(([code, title, body], index) => (
        <article class={`knowledge-layer layer-${index + 1}`}>
          <span>{code}</span>
          <h3>{title}</h3>
          <p>{body}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="knowledge-copy" data-reveal>
      <h2>知识不是聊天记录的总和。</h2>
      <p>Agent 先理解地图，再加载与任务有关的局部知识，必要时下钻真实来源。工作结束后，新的事实、决策和方法继续写回。</p>
      <div class="knowledge-definitions">
        <div><strong>Memory</strong><span>服务一个 Actor 的连续性</span></div>
        <div><strong>Knowledge</strong><span>服务整个组织的未来工作</span></div>
        <div><strong>History</strong><span>保存真实发生过的过程</span></div>
        <div><strong>Context</strong><span>为当前任务选择有效切片</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
